import firstpic from '../../images/svg-1.svg';
import secondpic from '../../images/svg-2.svg';
import thirdpic from '../../images/svg-3.svg';
import fourthpic from '../../images/svg-4.svg';
import fifthpic from '../../images/svg-5.svg';
import sixthpic from '../../images/svg-6.svg';

export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'home',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Home',
    headline: 'Traditional Jalisco Style Beef Birria',
    description: 'Sign up for our mailing list to receive notifications on our progress and locations once our food truck is up and running.',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: false,
    img: firstpic,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjTwo = {
    id: 'menu',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Menu',
    headline: 'Menu Items Below',
    description: 'Burritos, Tacos, Nachos, Fries',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: true,
    img: secondpic,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjThree = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'About',
    headline: 'Family owned and operated',
    description: 'Thanks for stopping by! We are Juan of a Kind, a Utah food truck, bringing you flavors from south of the border. We make a delicious birria, a traditional dish reserved for special occasions or celebrity events. We couple this classic slow simmered dish with a very well-known popular treat, the taco. We then sprinkle our very own secret cheese blend, and crisp it to perfection. The tender flavorful birria, warm gooey cheese served inside a crispy golden brown tortilla shell will have you coming back for more. Let’s face it, who can eat only one taco?',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: false,
    img: thirdpic,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjFour = {
    id: 'contact',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Contact',
    headline: 'Please see our contact information below',
    description: 'Do not hesitate to reach out for any inqiries',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: true,
    img: fourthpic,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjFive = {
    id: 'catering',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Catering',
    headline: 'Please fill out the information below',
    description: 'Please fill out the information fields to let us know a little bit more about your catering request and we will get back to you ',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: false,
    img: fifthpic,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};
